item.description:
It has been a while since we watched this movie and it is always good to get back to basics.
Please join us for a movie and discussion. The Movie will start at 6:45.It is OK if you are a little late. We will start on time in order to have time to discuss after the movie is over how we are using this on a regular basis. I always feel it is important the great things about this movie and to explain he things that need to be added to about this movie... Make you curious, then join us for a little conversation on how to intensify what is good to be even better!!!

Namaste~
Barb
